Lyric:
[by:小陀螺Tony]
[00:33.64]I thought we could be somethin',
[00:37.03]But you were just playin',
[00:38.91]You were just messin' with my head.
[00:44.10]I told you that I need you,
[00:46.63]You said you needed me too,
[00:49.16]Then why the fuck'd you hurt me instead?
[00:54.78]You made me so happy,
[00:57.00]I guess it's an illusion,
[00:59.93]I guess its a delusion, with regret.
[01:03.98]
[01:05.34]I thought we could be somethin',
[01:07.68]It turned out to be nothing,
[01:10.26]Now I'm all alone and I'm feelin' dead.
[01:15.97]You made me so breathless,
[01:18.30]But now I feel worthless,
[01:20.99]Out here on my own, and I'm feelin' dead.
[01:26.25]
[01:26.70]I want you so bad boy,
[01:28.47]To you I'm just a play toy,
[01:32.38]Now I'm all alone here in my bed.
[01:37.58]What is my existence? 
[01:39.71]In need of some assistance,
[01:42.29]Just wanna fill this void inside my head.
[01:48.30]I told you that I need you,
[01:50.33]You said you needed me too,
[01:53.06]You said you wouldn't hurt me,
[01:55.59]Yet you did.
[01:59.14]I thought we could be somethin',
[02:00.98]It turned out to be nothing,
[02:03.61]Now I'm all alone and I'm feelin' dead.
